318850931.text: "We find that insulin stimulated pGSK3beta and GSK3beta and pGSK3beta and beta-actin (pSerine9) are reduced in SWELL1 KO adipocytes (XREF_FIG), providing a molecular mechanism for the reduction in glycogen granules observed on EM (XREF_FIG)."
